{
  "id": "adv_card_aoi_52_02",
  "title": "井川葵",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 3.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "うん、いい天気。波もいい感じだね\nじゃあ、サーフボードを借りに行こうか",
      "startTime": 5.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 5.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "待った、葵。サーフボードって？\n俺、何も聞かされてないんだけど……",
      "startTime": 11.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.4686396281
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "言わなかったっけ？　サーフィンだよ\nこの旅行で挑戦してみたかったんだ。一緒にやろうよ",
      "startTime": 17.5686396281,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.8019713084
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "……ところで君、今からサーフィンをやるのに\nなんでいつもと同じスーツを着てるの？",
      "startTime": 26.6353046417,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "サーフィンをやるなんて知らなかったからな……\n俺、水着なんて持ってきてないぞ",
      "startTime": 31.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.4776864687
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "沖縄に来るのに、それはどうかと思うけど。でもまぁ\n格好なんて関係ないよ。そのままやればいいんじゃない",
      "startTime": 39.511019802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "良くない。水着を借りてくるよ。……それにしても\n葵はレッスンの時みたいな格好だな",
      "startTime": 48.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "これはラッシュガードだよ。マリンスポーツには\n日焼けや怪我がつきものだから",
      "startTime": 54.5166437784,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.783310445
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、全部莉央からの受け売りなんだけどね\n君もラッシュガードにしなよ。僕が選んであげるから",
      "startTime": 60.6166437784,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5433.3302816,
          "startTime": 66.04997406
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "―― 一時間後",
      "startTime": 64.949978129,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1500,
          "startTime": 66.449978129
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.0166407267
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "ふー。ちょっと休憩。サーフィンって、面白いね\n波に乗ることを『テイクオフ』って言うんだっけ？",
      "startTime": 73.4833048503,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "まだ三回に一回は失敗するけど、うまく波に乗れると\n最高の気分だね。そっちはどう？",
      "startTime": 81.2833048503,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.8499715169
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "俺は三回やって三回とも失敗だよ……\n葵はさすがだな。もうコツを掴んだのか？",
      "startTime": 88.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "コツって言われても、よく分からないけど\nここなら行ける、ってタイミングは掴めたかな",
      "startTime": 95.9201532046,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.1201532046
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "君の方は……波に乗れる頃には、日が暮れそうだね\n……そうだ。僕がサーフィンを教えてあげるよ",
      "startTime": 104.9201598166,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.9534865379
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、まずはパドリングからだよ\n姿勢を見てあげるから、横になって",
      "startTime": 111.0534865379,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "え、水の中じゃなくて、この砂浜で？\nいや、さすがに周りの人が見てるからちょっと……",
      "startTime": 117.4333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 12825.780232699997,
          "startTime": 130.259113566
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 121.4591069539
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "見てない見てない。ほら、早くここで横になって\n君は肩に力が入り過ぎなんだよ。ここをこうして……",
      "startTime": 126.0924402873,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5833.358255899995,
          "startTime": 131.9257985432
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9740.893046099998,
          "startTime": 135.8333333334
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっ、葵、そんな無理やり！　せめて変装してくれ\n……く、くすぐったい！　くすぐったいから……！",
      "startTime": 136.6666849773,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.0614272435
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（公衆の面前で葵の特別レッスンを受けた俺は）\n（ほんの少しサーフィンが出来るようになったのだった）",
      "startTime": 143.833324178,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 140.0614272435
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4618.715063600007,
          "startTime": 148.4520392416
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4618.715063600007,
          "startTime": 148.4520392416
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.4520392416
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ、サーフィンはこれくらいにして一休みするか\nまさか俺がサーファーになる日が来るとは",
      "startTime": 153.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "葵、教え方が意外とうまいな……あれ？\nそういえば葵がいない。確か、三十分前に……",
      "startTime": 162.5666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9944.494564999985,
          "startTime": 172.5111612317
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 162.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 168.1778278984
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "沖の方にいい波がきてるみたいなんだ\n僕、もう少し沖まで行ってくるから",
      "startTime": 172.0111556369,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11622.177696399973,
          "startTime": 183.6333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 175.4111612317
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 175.6444894788
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "と言っていたが、遅過ぎる……まさか水難事故？\n……葵ーー、どこだーー！",
      "startTime": 182.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 185.5288450875
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_52_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "（この辺りに葵はいなかった……）\n（もっと端の方まで探しに行かないと……）",
      "startTime": 188.0666554769,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4999.165359800003,
          "startTime": 190.5280104473
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5170.917510500004,
          "startTime": 193.2375729874
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 193.0375689185
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
